{"tid":1973280,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［又中］蕭若元：中聯辦已經少咗浦頭，已證明北京對港將採取懷柔策略！","createTime":"2020-04-15T05:59:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T07:17:53.000Z","uid":219007,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e97e7b59e8876c439d26897ad858643157d1238b","tid":1973280,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T05:59:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ICGz73w7vwY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FICGz73w7vwY&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQDsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=e0d9ee5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ICGz73w7vwY</a> <br />\n9/3/2020:<br />\n<br />\n雖然北京大策略上繼續維持不變，例如喺特赦訴求及普選訴求維持原有立場外，<span style=\"color: red;\">其他方面已經採取懷柔有路線。仲繼續覺得北京會強硬路線嘅如今已經證實錯晒。</span><br />\n<br />\n雖然警方繼續濫捕打人，但沒有超越上年11月的底線，已經冇咁嚴重，呢樣野係非常明顯。 林鄭亦都開始扮晒親民，扮吓打電話派錢，呢啲都係北京懷柔意思。<span style=\"color: red;\">如中聯辦亦都隱形左，駱惠寧都少咗鋪頭，原因係知道自己好乞人憎.....</span><br />\n<br />\n4月：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BaHfhAV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBaHfhAV.png&h=4d0fb8b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/38WGXAV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F38WGXAV.png&h=e51d77bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3595f6341b7ae26bc3c0978d14e39106fd94023","tid":1973280,"uid":244809,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:01:50.000Z","msg":"等佢出黎認錯，不過佢有錯都會認<br />\n好過某d人"},{"pid":"03736abac858494f87f716cf276933c6f8b27aff","tid":1973280,"uid":72830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:05:34.000Z","msg":"佢近排無講過中聯辦d野<br />\n就知佢唔想自打嘴巴<br />\n係燒山眼中只要唔係街度開機槍掃射其他野都係懷柔政策黎"},{"pid":"2b27095707a41ac3ebaf8279015b457833256c18","tid":1973280,"uid":196329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:09:14.000Z","msg":"拿 即係咁<br />\n任何事情都有唔同角度做解讀既<br />\ncritical thinking最緊要既係撇除自己既偏見先<br />\n呢個問題我首先要問你<br />\n<br />\n下刪一萬字